Package dalserver.conf

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PluginFactory
    PluginFactory provides methods to calculate specific values for particular metadata terms
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DbCreateConf
    A class for seeding a configuration file for a table that is already loaded into the database.
    DbCreateTable
    This base class for creating the database table that will be searched by a DAL service.
    DbLoadCSV
    a class for loading a CSV table into a database The table must be in comma-separated value format where the first line of the table provides the column names.
    DemoPluginFactory
    DemoPluginFactory demonstrates how to calculate specific values for particular metadata terms
    FITSHeaderKeywords
    a simple container for FITS Header keywords.
    KeywordConfig
    a class for configuring a KeywordFacotry with parameters and groups described in an XML file.
    MetadataExtractor
    MetadataExtractor extracts relevant metadata from supported data formats.
    MySQLCreateTable
    a class for creating tables in MySQL
    MySQLIngestTable
    a class for ingesting a simple catalog table into a MySQL database
    NTFITSHeaderKeywords
    a FITSHeaderKeywords container implemented on top of the nom.tam.fits.Header class.
    XMLConfiguredKeywordFactory
    a general purpose KeywordFactory that can be configured by an XML file
    XMLKeywordConfig
    a class for configuring a KeywordFacotry with parameters and groups described in an XML file.
    XMLv1KeywordConfig
    the parser class for our so-called version 1 of the XML keyword definition file.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DataFormatException
    an exception indicating that a dataset exhibited some illegal or inconsitant condition that prevent proper processing of its contents
    KeywordConfig.FormatException
    an exception indicating that the configuration file includes illegal or otherwise unparsable content for its assumed format.
